text: Pogonocherus ressli is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Holzschuh in 1977. It is known from Iran and Azerbaijan.BioLib.cz - Pogonocherus ressli. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1977
